# skills CLI 残留（如有人误用 pnpx skills add 时会生成）
.agents/

# .claude/skills/ —
#   - opendesign-*（4 个）  : 由 scripts/sync-opendesign-skills.js 从 atomgit 自动恢复（pnpm install / dev 触发）
#   - 项目自有 5 个        : 入 git，直接维护
.claude/skills/*/
!.claude/skills/meta-tags-optimizer/
!.claude/skills/schema-markup-generator/
!.claude/skills/sitemap-meta-tags-batch-generator/
!.claude/skills/sitemap-schema-batch-generator/
!.claude/skills/vue-best-practices/

# CodeGraph MCP server artifacts (local tool, not business code)
.codegraph/
